  <App />
</ThemeContext.Provider>
 Project Idea: Global theme switcher, auth user context, language selector.

ğŸ—‚ Step 3: Redux Toolkit (RTK)
Skip old Redux boilerplate â€” RTK is simpler & faster.

Core concepts:

Store â†’ All app state

Slice â†’ State + reducers

Dispatch â†’ Trigger actions

Selector â†’ Read state

syntax:
