  name: 'counter',
  initialState: { value: 0 },
  reducers: {
    increment: state => { state.value += 1 }
  }
});
 Project Idea: Multi-slice app â€” counter + cart + products.
ğŸ’¡ Start with: counterSlice â†’ increment, decrement, reset.

ğŸ—‚ Step 4:  Async State with createAsyncThunk
RTKâ€™s built-in async helper â†’ perfect for fetching + handling loading/errors.
syntax:
